#: server.py:637
msgid ""
"\n"
"    该函数是CVE修复流程的第六步，必须严格按照顺序执行（仅当第五步补丁应用成功后才可执行）：\n"
"        1. 对于第五步中修复成功的分支，创建并提交Pull Request\n"
"        2. 参数说明：\n"
"           - branch: 受影响分支名，作为提交PR的目标分支\n"
"           - repo_url: 目标仓库URL（必须由用户显式提供）\n"
"           - fork_repo_url: fork仓库URL\n"
"           - clone_dir: 本地克隆目录，必须与第四步/第五步使用的 clone_dir 保持一致\n"
"        3. 执行PR创建操作：\n"
"           - 创建PR标题（包含CVE ID和分支信息）\n"
"           - 创建PR描述（包含修复详情）\n"
"           - 提交PR到目标仓库\n"
"        4. 明确反馈执行结果：\n"
"           - PR是否创建成功\n"
"           - PR的完整URL链接\n"
"           - PR编号和标题\n"
"           - 如果失败，明确告知失败原因\n"
"        5. 对于第五步中每个成功应用补丁的分支，都需要单独调用此函数创建PR\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    This function is the sixth step in the CVE remediation process and "
"must be executed strictly in order (only after patch application is "
"successful in step 5):\n"
"        1. For branches successfully fixed in step 5, create and submit a"
" Pull Request\n"
"        2. Parameter description:\n"
"           - branch: Affected branch name, used as the target branch for "
"PR submission\n"
"           - repo_url: Target repository URL (must be explicitly provided"
" by the user)\n"
"           - fork_repo_url: Fork repository URL\n"
"           - clone_dir: Local clone directory, which must be consistent "
"with the clone_dir used in steps 4 and 5\n"
"        3. Execute PR creation operation:\n"
"           - Create PR title (including CVE ID and branch information)\n"
"           - Create PR description (including fix details)\n"
"           - Submit PR to the target repository\n"
"        4. Clearly report the execution results:\n"
"           - Whether PR creation was successful\n"
"           - Complete URL link of the PR\n"
"           - PR number and title\n"
"           - If failed, clearly inform the failure reason\n"
"        5. For each branch that successfully applied patches in step 5, "
"this function must be called separately to create PR\n"
"    "

